version_description:
[New features]
1. Supports brand new DJI MAVIC 2 Enterprise Dual.
2. Supports the area and spot temperature measurement feature of MAVIC 2 Enterprise Dual.
3. Supports the high-temperature alert feature of MAVIC 2 Enterprise Dual.
[Optimizations]
1. Improves sound transmission speed of speakers.
2. Fixes certain issues and optimizes overall app quality.
